fields.name: MaxNumberOfRecordSets
fields.description: The maximum number of record sets that can be created in this Private DNS zone. This is a read-only property and any attempt to set this value will be ignored.

fields.name: MaxNumberOfVirtualNetworkLinks
fields.description: The maximum number of virtual networks that can be linked to this Private DNS zone. This is a read-only property and any attempt to set this value will be ignored.

fields.name: MaxNumberOfVirtualNetworkLinksWithRegistration
fields.description: The maximum number of virtual networks that can be linked to this Private DNS zone with registration enabled. This is a read-only property and any attempt to set this value will be ignored.

fields.name: NumberOfRecordSets
fields.description: The current number of record sets in this Private DNS zone. This is a read-only property and any attempt to set this value will be ignored.

fields.name: NumberOfVirtualNetworkLinks
fields.description: The current number of virtual networks that are linked to this Private DNS zone. This is a read-only property and any attempt to set this value will be ignored.

fields.name: NumberOfVirtualNetworkLinksWithRegistration
fields.description: The current number of virtual networks that are linked to this Private DNS zone with registration enabled. This is a read-only property and any attempt to set this value will be ignored.

fields.name: ProvisioningState
fields.description: The provisioning state of the resource. This is a read-only property and any attempt to set this value will be ignored.
